[{"title":"Maverick","url":"/2022/06/18/Maverick/","content":"<h3 id=\"Jrohy’s-Trojan-可视化面板\"><a href=\"#Jrohy’s-Trojan-可视化面板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Jrohy’s Trojan 可视化面板\"></a>Jrohy’s Trojan 可视化面板</h3><p>Jrohy’s Trojan 可视化面板部署 + Jinwyp’s Linux Kernel Installing + 添加可视化面板伪装站点及端口</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash &lt;(curl -Lso- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MatthewJian/Maverick/main/Installation/Tro-install.sh)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>添加可视化面板伪装站点</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash &lt;(curl -Lso- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MatthewJian/Maverick/main/Modification/Addwebsite.sh)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Atrandys’-Trojan\"><a href=\"#Atrandys’-Trojan\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Atrandys’ Trojan\"></a><strong>Atrandys’ Trojan</strong></h3><p>Atrandys’ Trojan 部署 + Jinwyp’s Linux Kernel Installing + 修改伪装站点</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash &lt;(curl -Lso- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MatthewJian/Maverick/main/Installation/Tro-install-at.sh)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>修改 Trojan 端口及密码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nano /usr/src/trojan/server.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Vaxilu’s-X-ui-多协议多用户-Xray-面板\"><a href=\"#Vaxilu’s-X-ui-多协议多用户-Xray-面板\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vaxilu’s X-ui 多协议多用户 Xray 面板\"></a><strong>Vaxilu’s X-ui 多协议多用户 Xray 面板</strong></h3><p>Atrandys’ Trojan 部署 + Jinwyp’s Linux Kernel Installing</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bash &lt;(curl -sL https://wws.lcd.im/wwwx/trovins.sh)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","tags":["Maverick"]}]